Let me introduce myself, Walid Bellagha, better known as Maroki Rider,
creator and host of the YouTube channel Maroki Rider.



Created in November 2017, my channel talks about motorcycles with more
than 100,000 subscribers and aims to make young people aware of the
dangers and obligations they have to become real bikers. In one year
of existence, I managed to mobilize a faithful audience that looks
forward to the arrival of each new video. On average, each counts 100
000 views. On the other hand, I bring to your attention that I also
have an Instagram account with more than 28,000 subscribers and
Facebook account with more than 21,000 subscribers.



If I allow myself today to contact you, it’s to offer you a partnership
between my channel and your brand. It would be a great oppurtunity for me
to test ride your electric scooter and make a review of it .


Thanks to the audiences of my channel, you will be able to reach a lot of
targets sensitive to these values and thus push your mark with consumers
convinced by what it conveys. For my part, a partnership with a brand of
your size will allow me to develop my project.

explain in more detail my motives and, for this purpose, remain at your
disposal.
